Grammar notes.
Related vocabulary: to withhold, stereotypical, ethnicity.
1. My boss withheld my salary for two months until his tax troubles had been resolved.
2. A man in a bowler hat, drinking tea is&nbsp;a stereotypical view of an English man.
3. My ethnicity is English, though my blood is mixed.]]></itunes:subtitle>



