h the binoculars, I spotted a golden eagle.2. The bus&nbsp;slowed down and turned into the parking lot.3. The parrot outlived two owners before it eventually&nbsp;died.4.&nbsp;"Children, it's dark. Don't let me catch you sneaking out!"&nbsp;]]></itunes:subtitle>



