am was the home team with the advantage of the local people cheering for them.2. The spectators were standing up throughout the game; I could barely see any of it because they were in the way.3. The new player shot many times, but only made two baskets.4. The home team's logo is painted on the court in shiny red letters.]]></itunes:subtitle>



